        <div class="td-post-content">

        <div class="td-post-featured-image"><figure><img width="696" height="391" class="entry-thumb" src="https://www.juventusnews24.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/pjanic-juventus-champions-league-settembre-2016.jpg" srcset="https://www.juventusnews24.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/pjanic-juventus-champions-league-settembre-2016.jpg 696w, https://www.juventusnews24.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/pjanic-juventus-champions-league-settembre-2016-300x169.jpg 300w, https://www.juventusnews24.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/pjanic-juventus-champions-league-settembre-2016-128x72.jpg 128w, https://www.juventusnews24.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/02/pjanic-juventus-champions-league-settembre-2016-32x18.jpg 32w" sizes="(max-width: 696px) 100vw, 696px" alt="pjanic" title="pjanic-juventus-champions-league-settembre-2016" atomik-pl="atomik/x6o1s8a62tx77j8o7cxgj0t1b" /><figcaption class="wp-caption-text">&copy; foto www.imagephotoagency.it</figcaption></figure></div>
        <div class="at-above-post addthis_tool" data-url="https://www.juventusnews24.com/pjanic-infortunio-ultimi-aggiornamenti/"></div><h2>Infortunio Pjanic, c&#8217;è il comunicato ufficiale della Juventus: lesione di tipo distrattivo al quadricipite femorale della coscia destra. Le ultime notizie &#8211; ore 15:00</h2>






